<br />
Klopp: &quot;Meanwhile, they don&rsquo;t have to sell players any more so, I&rsquo;m always a little bit too late. There's nothing to say about this.&rdquo;

Klopp on AFCON changes: &quot;It's fantastic. When we signed Salah we thought 'oh my god' we'll lose 2 in winter time. Now we won't lose them.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;Being honest, I don't like to travel in pre-season but we have to and now we're here it's nice. Much better than I thought.&quot;

Lallana on Henderson's return: &quot;It's great having him back. We're best of mates and we've missed him massively.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp on Lallana: &quot;He was my neighbour but now he's moved. I don't think it was because of me.&quot;
